/td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Community Raid: POH 3/10/01</span><hr size=1> An open community Plane of Hate raid lead by Cauis Britannicus on the 10th of March meeting up at the Wizard portal pad in the Desert of Southern Ro at 12:30pm EST 10:30am PST.  All non-wizards are required to bring 50pp for their hate stones.<br>
<br>
The Maximum duration of this raid will be 8 hours.  Please plan accordingly and bring plenty of food and water.  All coin loot will go to one person on the raid to be distributed between the clerics / wizards / enchanters.  All rare gems will be randomed for by group leader first and then by group members of the winning leaders group, I reserve the first 4 rare type gems to give to the wizards as they come up to hate with no loot expected.  All class specific armor will be randomed between the class that will wear it.  Once a member of that class wins an item they will be excluded from rolling until all members of that class have won an item.  This excludes class breast plates which everyone in that class will roll on no matter what they have won.  I reserve the right to reward any one person with any drop item.  This shall exclude god/boss loot which will be rolled on between the users of dropped items.  In the event that we have to call for replacements, they will be on a 2 hour loot timer that will not allow them to loot until those 2 hours are up.  This is to avoid people popping in after the break and receiving loot with no time involved.<br>
<br>
I ask that you stay the duration and pull all the inhabitants of hate to be fair to all classes present.  Anyone found to be leaving the raid because of a death or because the received a peice of loot will not be invited back in the future for further raids to be.<br>
<br>
If you have any questions I can be contacted at cauis-britannicus@home.com<br>
<br>
